'''蓋·愛德華·皮爾斯'''（{{lang-en|Guy Edward Pearce}}，{{bd|1967年|10月5日}}） 是一名[[澳大利亚|澳大利亚]][[男演员|男演员]]<ref>{{Cite web|author=Gary Dretzka|work=Movie City News|title=An Interview With Guy Pearce|url=http://www.moviecitynews.com/Interviews/pearce.html|accessdate=15 February 2009|date=1 June 2003|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20081115051601/http://www.moviecitynews.com/Interviews/pearce.html|archivedate=2008年11月15日}} </ref>，他主演最知名的作品是2001年由[[克里斯托弗·诺兰|克里斯托弗·诺兰]]导演的《[[记忆碎片|记忆碎片]]》。

== 早年生活 ==
他的母亲Anne Cocking（娘家姓Pickering）是一名生于[[達勒姆郡|達勒姆郡]]的教师；父亲Stuart Pearce是个生于[[新西兰|新西兰]]的[[空军|空军]]测试[[飞行员|飞行员]]，但在皮尔斯9岁时就去世了<ref>{{Cite news | url=http://film.guardian.co.uk/interview/interviewpages/0,,2025921,00.html | work=The Guardian | location=London | title=Portrait of the artist | date=4 March 2007 | accessdate=4 May 2010 | first=Chrissy | last=Iley | archive-date=2007-03-15 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20070315084837/http://film.guardian.co.uk/interview/interviewpages/0,,2025921,00.html | dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.tiscali.co.uk/entertainment/film/biographies/guy_pearce_biog.html |title=Guy Pearce biography |publisher=Tiscali.co.uk |date= |accessdate=13 April 2011 |archive-date=2009-02-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090207090337/http://www.tiscali.co.uk/entertainment/film/biographies/guy_pearce_biog.html |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.filmreference.com/film/14/Guy-Pearce.html |title=Guy Pearce Biography (1967–) |publisher=Filmreference.com |date= |accessdate=13 April 2011 |archive-date=2016-03-03 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160303215357/http://www.filmreference.com/film/14/Guy-Pearce.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。在他三岁时，他家搬到了[[澳洲|澳洲]]的[[吉朗_(维多利亚州)|吉朗]]，在那里他母亲经营着一家[[鹿|鹿]]场。他进入当地的私人学校 ''The Geelong College'' 就读，并且是GSODA的成员。15到22岁之间，他是一名[[健美|健美]]业余选手。此外，他也参与过[[击剑|击剑]]运动。

1980年代后期，他居住在维多利亚州的Box Hill North，并参与了澳洲电视剧《Neighbours》的演出。

== 个人生活 ==
1997年3月，他与[[心理学家|心理学家]]Kate Mestitz结婚<ref>[http://www.moviemaker.com/articles/item/the_adventures_of_guy_pearce_2997/ The Adventures of Guy Pearce] {{webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120304130518/http://www.moviemaker.com/directing/article/the_adventures_of_guy_pearce_2997/ |date=2012-03-04 }}. ''[[MovieMaker_Magazine|MovieMaker Magazine]]''.</ref>。他是{{le|吉朗澳式足球会|Geelong Football Club}}（Geelong Football Club，[[澳大利亞澳式足球聯盟|澳大利亞澳式足球聯盟]]的球队之一）的长期支持者<ref>[http://gfc.com.au/default.asp?pg=insidetheclub&spg=socialclub&articleid=241777 Geelong Football Club] {{webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20040610140040/http://gfc.com.au/default.asp?pg=insidetheclub |date=2004-06-10 }}</ref>。他个人不信[[上帝|上帝]]属于[[无神论者|无神论者]]，不过却信仰“我们人类彼此都是相互关联的”(''we're all connected'')信念<ref>"I've got a T-shirt that says, 'Jesus saves,' and the 's' in 'Jesus' is a big dollar sign," he says. "I've worn it here [in America] and had people come up on the street and go, 'You can't wear that.' People in Australia think it's funny. I'm fascinated by religion. I don't believe in God, but the thing I do believe in is that we're all connected.{{Cite news | url=http://www.latimes.com/entertainment/news/la-et-pearce27-2008aug27,0,7893219.story | title=Actor Guy Pearce is all about the details | work=Los Angeles Times | first=Cristy | last=Lytal | date=27 August 2008 | accessdate=4 May 2010 | archive-date=2008-12-01 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20081201104244/http://www.latimes.com/entertainment/news/la-et-pearce27-2008aug27%2C0%2C7893219.story | dead-url=no }}</ref>。

